-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In order to compile  code
type command
 
make
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In order to run code
type command
 
make run
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In order to remove generated object files
type command
 
make clean
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1)It will ask for a path of image with name

2)Give path of image and it will display Menu

3)Select any choice from the Menu to get the output of respective method

4)In order to go to menu hit enter.

5)Repeat process 1,2,3,4 for another image(basel_gray.bmp)
 
6)In order to exit press 4 after menu get displayed

